{"data":[{"id":560702729,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"81a939e058786b6db7cf322b6ba78a43","url_token":"ni-ning-tian-kong","name":"泥泞天空","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/1dc3c0bb43162b6863dac9cfdac32488_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/1dc3c0bb43162b6863dac9cfdac32488_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/81a939e058786b6db7cf322b6ba78a43","user_type":"people","headline":"且听我胡说八道！","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":7388,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560702729","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545880565,"updated_time":1545880565,"extras":"","is_copyable":false,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":17,"comment_count":5,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"need_payment","content":"\u003cp\u003e惊闻近日网络上有大量沙雕网友玩梗高中生网友证明“哥德巴赫猜想”，我深感痛惜！我曾有幸在2016年看过大数学家陈景润先生为《初等数论》一书写的序言，好不欢喜(两手翻花)。看着网友们的恶搞，你们好笑我是笑不出来，我这个眼泪在肚子里，我笑不出来。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e数学不是胡学，哥猜不是乱猜。\u003cbr\u003e哥德巴赫猜想并非不能证明，我研究哥猜20年了，大大小小的问题我都研究，我太了解它了！\u003cbr\u003e我刚刚打开知乎的时候，还有个知友问我，哥德巴赫猜想到底能不能证明啊？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不懂数学的网友还在笑，我是笑不出来。\u003cbr\u003e有的网友一看到“哥德巴赫猜想”，第一反应“哇，太难了！”这怎么行呢？见到这些世界级的数学难题，尤其需要勇于证明，从精神上藐视它。\u003cbr\u003e我们说一个学过数学的人不敢向世界级数学难题发起挑战是可悲的，有了挑战的勇气不能把它证明就是可耻的。\u003cbr\u003e我看有些学数学的，学神竟然和学霸谈起了恋爱，学霸叫学神叫“婶婶”，学神叫学霸叫“爸爸”，婶侄不分，父妻颠倒。\u003cbr\u003e这样的关系是乱伦的！是要给所有学数学的人谢罪的！\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e喜闻一位高中生最近要在知乎上发表证明“哥德巴赫猜想”的论文，祝贺这位同学，这与这位同学长期的勤奋研究是分不开的。说到勤奋，我就想到正在网上认真学习研究“留学”勤奋写论文的我。今年下半年，“留学”研究会亲自举办的第一届“留学”生毕业典礼即将举行，我将作为第一届“留学”毕业生代表出席此次典礼，并认真发表关于“留学”研究的诸多感悟。生活学习两开花，弘扬“留学”文化，希望大家多多参加。\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"惊闻近日网络上有大量沙雕网友玩梗高中生网友证明“哥德巴赫猜想”，我深感痛惜！我曾有幸在2016年看过大数学家陈景润先生为《初等数论》一书写的序言，好不欢喜(两手翻花)。看着网友们的恶搞，你们好笑我是笑不出来，我这个眼泪在肚子里，我笑不出来。数学…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=206\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_